The App may automatically collect certain information upon installation and use, including:
- your device’s IP address;
- pages you visit within the App, including date, time, and session duration;
- your device’s operating system;
- time spent submitting a request.
The App does not collect precise location data.
The Service Provider may request personal information such as your email address solely for providing app functionality, notifications, or feedback. All data is used in accordance with this policy.

The App may share aggregated and anonymized data with third parties to improve service quality.
The Service Provider may disclose data:
- as required by law;
- to protect the rights and safety of users;
- to trusted third-party service providers acting on behalf of the Service Provider and bound by confidentiality obligations.
